{"tid":818790,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【🌋樓爆2018】molamola😭❗業主大劈$380萬要錢唔要貨❗淡淡等跌八成","createTime":"2018-09-14T10:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T09:50:49.000Z","uid":43146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8db5e372afe73be975279f542ad825eabf4c5289","tid":818790,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:40:05.000Z","msg":"二手樓交投再陷新冰河時間，等錢使業主紛減價，甚至出現剛簽租約單位亦劈價求售。<br />\n<br />\n有九龍站地產代理指，天璽海鑽璽中層B室，實用面積1,128方呎，4房間隔，享海景，一直放租放賣，賣價4,880萬元，本月初劈16%以6.7萬元租出，呎租失守60元。業主為內地客，有指急於套現，現減價380萬至4,500萬元連租約出售，呎價39,894元。<br />\n<br />\n該代理坦言，高鐵將通車對九龍站樓市未見刺激作用，本月二手成交量僅兩宗，形容處於「冰河」。<br />\n<br />\n記者:朱連峰<br />\n<br />\n全球樓行 Dream House零距離<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&d=3yIU3YvVbR2hif99R5thyy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=18f624bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&h=9bc132df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty</a>"},{"pid":"4a4b85512dffc5ce451d87a441b1d825c72a0106","tid":818790,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:42:02.000Z","msg":"急套現唔計"},{"pid":"264d39bfaa2d6b9c99e7ec4850001b1960fd844b","tid":818790,"uid":153778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:43:34.000Z","msg":"高鐵通車個消息一撚早消化完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb8cbdad465a74aa795d2eafde49ca36ecc9ebc","tid":818790,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4a4b85512dffc5ce451d87a441b1d825c72a0106","tid":818790,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:42:02.000Z","msg":"急套現唔計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:50:32.000Z","msg":"點先計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ce723408ee4e033eedc15b366052dd8f